## ğŸ“‹ Quick Start

### Deploy Locally with Docker

```powershell
cd d:\SMS\student-management-system
.\DOCKER.ps1 -Start
```

**Expected output:**
```
==================================================
  Starting SMS Application
==================================================

â„¹ Image not found, building...
â„¹ This may take 5-10 minutes on first time...
```

